          <h3>
            <a href="../../../users/me/favorites" class="favorite favorite_627"><span>*</span></a>
            
              <a href="http://www.linuxplumbersconf.org/2010/ocw/proposals/627" class="title">A new perspective on virtuality: View-OS</a>
            
            
          </h3>

          <div class="excerpt">
            Umview and Kmview are partial virtual machine monitors. Users (not administrators) can safely define for each process its own file system, networking support, devices, user-id, time, etc.
	    
          </div>
	  
